window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>\"As I sleep, my mind will erase everything I did today. I will wake up tomorrow as I did this morning. Thinking I'm still a child. Thinking I have a whole lifetime of choice ahead of me....\" </p> <p>Memories define us. </p> <p>So what if you lost yours every time you went to sleep? </p> <p>Your name, your identity, your past, even the people you love - all forgotten overnight. </p> <p>And the one person you trust may be telling you only half the story. </p> <p>Welcome to Christine's life.</p>"; 
